1. 只要設定變數 url
2. 滑鼠點一下即可重新載入


********** url 參數設定 **********

google 簡報參數：
loop=true      循環播放
delayms=20000  每頁停留時間(毫秒)
rm=minimal     隱藏控制列
start=true     自動播放

範例：
https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/e/2PACX-1vT0upFE11b8SlwpGLJx4fHjTkYTlMQW2fFGAsph1gOjUjM9U2QeuXcxZIIElVH1jduKywQQZlOz_Hue/embed?loop=true&delayms=20000&rm=minimal&start=true

------------------------------------------------

youtube 參數：
https://developers.google.com/youtube/iframe_api_reference
https://developers.google.com/youtube/player_parameters
https://www.h3xed.com/web-and-internet/link-directly-to-and-embed-hd-youtube-videos
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7582336/force-youtube-embed-to-start-in-720p?utm_medium=organic&utm_source=google_rich_qa&utm_campaign=google_rich_qa
https://www.techmarks.com/muteyoutubevideoplayer/
http://ashblagdon.com/how-to-get-your-embedded-youtube-videos-to-autoplay-on-your-website/
autoplay=1        自動開始播放
loop=1            循環播放
controls=0        隱藏控制列
showinfo=1        顯示資訊(html5 player 似乎沒作用)
mute=0            是否靜音
cc_load_policy=1  是否強制開啟字幕
VQ=HD720 HD1080   強制以 720P 1080P 播放
list=             播放清單 ID
rel=0             是否在片尾顯示推薦影片

範例：
https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?autoplay=1&loop=1&controls=0&showinfo=1&mute=0&cc_load_policy=1&VQ=HD720&list=播放清單ID


https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?autoplay=1&loop=1&controls=0&showinfo=1&mute=0&cc_load_policy=1&VQ=HD720&list=PLZ9f87PcBj_jCQWBrvhLvZCQHtRJoUGrn


單一影片
https://www.youtube.com/embed/nEVnAeuRWQo?autoplay=1&loop=1&controls=0&showinfo=1&mute=0&cc_load_policy=1&VQ=HD720

https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/nEVnAeuRWQo?rel=0&amp;controls=0&autoplay=1&loop=1&showinfo=1&VQ=HD1080